            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Contaminations from alpha0(12C) and tau0(13C)",
                "prevented extraction of the a0 group at angles beyond",
                "theta c.m. = 165 at 17 and 18 MeV. The relatively",
                "large errors near the regions of 16.2 MeV and 17.8",
                "MeV are due to corrections to the alpha-particle",
                "yield for elastic scattering contributions from 12C",
                "and 13C respectively."
              ]
